# UI Production Grade Rule

## Layout

- All app pages MUST use a dashboard layout, not a landing hero.
- Max 2 primary columns.
- Use 8pt spacing system.
- No section without clear purpose.

## Typography

- H1 only used for landing pages.
- Dashboard uses:
  - H2 (section title)
  - H3 (card title)
  - body (description)

## Hierarchy

Every page MUST define:

1. Primary action (1 only)
2. Secondary actions (max 4)
3. Supporting info

## Components

- Must use reusable components:
  - Card
  - StatCard
  - ActionCard
  - EmptyState
  - SectionHeader

## Forbidden

- Hero-only layout in app pages
- Oversized typography
- Random pill button groups
- Empty placeholder without UX meaning